citeinfo.title: Multichannel Seismic-Reflection Profiles Eastern Gulf of Alaska USGS open file report 87-148

descript.abstract: Approximately 2,108 km of 24-channel seismic-reflection profiles in the Eastern Gulf of Alaska are now available for purchase from the National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC). These profiles were collected during the summer of 1978 aboard the R/V S.P. Lee, Cruise L3-78-EG, by the U.S. Geological Survey (USGS), Department of Interior.
